window.bookSummaryJSON = "The quick-witted, good-natured detective Mma \"Precious\" Ramotswe shines in this irresistible best seller. It continues the charming series that began with <i>The No. 1 Ladies' Detective Agency</i>, hailed as one of the \"International Books of the Year and the Millennium\" by the <i>Times Literary Supplement</i> <p>Between intriguing new cases and troubling personal developments, Precious' hands are full. The four Miss Beauty and Integrity pageant finalists may have questionable moral fiber, and the brother of an important government worker has allegedly been poisoned. On top of all that, Precious' reliable fianci might be hiding something.</p> <p>Life is more difficult than ever at the No. 1 Ladies' Detective Agency, but it's nothing a little clear thinking and a few mugs of bush tea can't candle.</p>"; 
